---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for Health and Safety Kits. We respect your privacy and do not use tracking cookies.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 700px;">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We use <a href="https://umami.is" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Umami</a>, a privacy-friendly
        analytics tool. Umami does not use cookies, does not collect personal data, and is fully
        GDPR compliant. We use it only to understand which pages are visited and how visitors find our site.
      </p>

      <h2>Payments</h2>
      <p>
        All payments are processed by <a href="https://gumroad.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gumroad</a>.
        We do not store your payment information. Please refer to
        <a href="https://gumroad.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gumroad&rsquo;s privacy policy</a>
        for details on how they handle your data.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Form</h2>
      <p>
        If you use our contact form, your name, email, and message are processed by Netlify Forms.
        We use this information solely to respond to your enquiry and do not share it with third parties.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This website does not use tracking cookies. No personal data is collected through cookies.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        If you have submitted information through our contact form and wish to have it deleted,
        please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
